COMMENT ON TABLE finance.economic_nexus_monitoring IS 'Rolling 12-month trailing revenue and transaction counts per state for economic nexus threshold monitoring. Updated by the Rust tax service after each taxable transaction. revenue_threshold_pct is a generated column enabling the dashboard to instantly show which states are at 75%+, 90%+, or 100% of the nexus threshold without a JOIN. When nexus_triggered = true the compliance team is alerted to register in the jurisdiction before collecting further revenue.';


