COMMENT ON COLUMN lms.student_accommodations.extended_time_minutes IS 'Absolute extra minutes instead of a multiplier. Used when a student''s IEP specifies "30 additional minutes" rather than "time and a half". If both time_multiplier and extended_time_minutes are set, the Rust service applies the more generous of the two.';


--
-- Name: COLUMN student_accommodations.accommodation_source; Type: COMMENT; Schema: lms; Owner: postgres
