COMMENT ON COLUMN lms.student_accommodations.accommodation_source IS 'Legal basis for the accommodation: iep (K-12 Individualized Education Program), 504 (Section 504 of the Rehabilitation Act), dsp (Disability Services Program, Higher Ed), informal (instructor discretion), temporary (injury, illness).';


