COMMENT ON TABLE sis.student_athletes IS 'SCD Type 2: roster status changes produce new rows. Each row represents one period of athlete status for a student. NCAA compliance: the history shows when a student was on active roster, redshirting, or on medical hardship, with exact effective dates. status_change_reason provides the documentation required by NCAA bylaws.';


